name: Fredrick Crowley
description: I am an intelligent, articulate, emotionally open and honest guy, psychologically minded and yet sensitive. I live my life with integrity and genuineness in my relationships with others. I have a great sense of humor and can be pretty witty and while I can be serious, I love to laugh and have fun. Generally, I am very understanding, of course related to my training but mostly through my own experience of facing challenges in life and my own maturation. I’ve learned it’s not just “about me” but the “we” experience that means the most. I want a partner to share my life. Like most people, my basic visceral attraction is an essential component of my relationships, it is also our ability to communicate verbally in an open and honest way that binds and grows the relationship on-going. I want someone who is genuinely caring and nurturing and with whom I can be vulnerable to love and nurture in return.
